- Break times and review sessions
- Practice test timing
- Priority topics by difficulty
- Final review schedule
```

### 48. Test Anxiety Reducer
```
I get anxious before tests. Provide strategies for:
- Pre-test preparation routines
- During-test calming techniques
- Time management methods
- Positive self-talk scripts
- Physical relaxation exercises
```

### 49. Practice Test Creator
```
Create a practice test for [subject] covering [topics]. Include:
- [number] multiple choice questions
- [number] short answer questions
- [number] essay questions
- Answer key with explanations
- Scoring rubric
```

### 50. Memory Retrieval Practice
```
Help me practice recalling [topic] through:
- Quick-fire questions
- Fill-in-the-blank exercises
- Concept matching games
- Application scenarios
- Self-quizzing techniques
```

### 51. Test-Taking Strategy Coach
```
Provide test-taking strategies for [subject] including:
- Time allocation per section
- Question analysis methods
- Process of elimination
- When to skip and return
- Final review techniques
```

### 52. Weakness Identifier
```
